Endless Loop:
    The loop's expression is true forever.

While-else:
    Format:
        while Expression1:
            Statement1
        else:
            Statement2

    Analyse:
        If the expression is false, the statement2 will be executed.


For:
    Format:
        for Variable in Collection:
            Statement

    Analyse:
        Take each element in the collection in order and copy it to the variable,then execute the statement, and so on and so on,util the last element in collection


range([start], end, [step]):
    to generate the sequence








































